Vietnam from 1980 to 1982, said he was impressed by the 
remarkable changes in Vietnam. Ajit Singh and Cam later 
adjourned for closed-door talks at the same venue. 
  Earlier, while waiting for Ajit Singh, Cam told reporters 
they would discuss [words indistinct] Vietnam cooperation in 
training and communications, among other things. [passage 
omitted] 

