belonging to the U.S. Air Force present in South Korea and the 
puppet Air Force. Flying above Yongwol, Chongju and Yesan of 
South Korea, they staged exercises of a surprise bombing on 
targets, a support to ground attack, a long-distance movement, 
entry into war and an aerial attack. 
