<F P=102>  SK2102113094 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1018 GMT 21 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2102113094 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, February 21 (KCNA) -- The dear leader 
Comrade Kim Chong-il sent a 60th birthday table to Chon 
Chae-yun, head of the Kim Chong-tae Electric Locomotive General 
Enterprise Branch of the Rolling Stock Design Office under the 
Ministry of Railways. 
  Chon Chae-yun, a labour hero and a merited designer, 
projected "Red Flag No. 1", the first electric locomotive in 
Korea, and is now devoting himself to introducing heavy rail, 
mordernizing railways and consolidating the material and 
technical foundations of railways. 

</TEXT>

