<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, February 23 (KCNA) -- The U.S. 
imperialists Monday committed an aerial photographing and 
electronic reconnaissance on the strategic depth and inland 
areas of the DPRK with an Okinawa-based RC-135 strategic 
reconnaissance plane in the skies above Pochon, Yanggu and 
Kansong, South Korea, along the Military Demarcation Line, 
