  That day large-calibre artillery units and armed bandits of 
the South Korean puppet army incited a war atmosphere, firing 
hundreds of bullets and shells in the areas adjacent to the 
demilitarized zone in Yonchon, Paju and Chorwon Counties, and 
formations of helicopter gunboats and transports of the puppet 
army staged an exercise of support and transport for ground 
attack units. 
