pushing aside all manners of intervention and pressure of 
outside forces. 
  Pursuing non-aligned policy externally, Guyana is developing 
friendly relations with foreign countries and making efforts to 
establish a new international economic order. 
  Though Korea and Guyana are geographically far away from 
each 
other, the peoples of the two countries are developing the bonds 
of friendship. 
  The Korean people believe that the friendly and cooperative 
relations between Korea and Guyana will further expand and 
develop in the common interests of the two peoples. 
  The Korean people extend congratulatory greetings to the 
Guyanese people on the day of the proclamation of the republic 
and wish them great success in their future work to build a new 
prosperous society. 

