<H3> <TI>   Kim Chong-il's `Famous' Works Published Abroad </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK2402050294 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0425 GMT 24 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2402050294 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, February 24 (KCNA) -- The dear leader 
Comrade Kim Chong-il's famous work "Abuses of Socialism Are 
Intolerable" was published in booklet by the Cerberus publishing 
house of Hungary and the Datina publishing house of Romania on 
the occasion of his birthday. 
  The Kultura publishing house of Yugoslavia published in 
booklet his work "The Workers' Party of Korea Organizes and 
Guides All Victories of Our People." 
  In the preface of the booklet, the publishing house says 
this 
work, on the basis of a scientific analysis of the lawful 
requirement of the present time and the cause of socialism, 
expounds questions of principle in the building of the 
revolutionary party of the working class, including defence of 
the revolutionary character of the party and the strengthening 
of the unity and cohesion of the party and the relations between 
the party and the masses. 
  A seminar on his work "Our Socialism Centred on the Masses 
Shall Not Perish" was held at the Nicaraguan committee for the 
study of the chuche idea and a seminar on his works "On the 
Fundamentals of Revolutionary Party Building" and "Abuses of 
Socialism Are Intolerable" at the Peruvian Group for the Study 
of the Literary and Art Idea of Comrade Kim Chong-il. 

</TEXT>

