<H3> <TI>   Vice Premier Discusses Technology in Thailand </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW2202171694 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1504 GMT 22 Feb 
94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW2202171694 </F>
