<H3> <TI>   `First' Joint Venture With U.S. Inaugurated </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW2302183894 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1635 GMT 23 Feb 
94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW2302183894 </F>
<F P=104>  Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, February 23 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- In the 
city of Princeton in the New Jersey State of the USA there has 
been held the ceremony of opening the first Mongolian American 
joint venture "Mongolian Tourism Corporation of America" which 
was set up by the Mongolian "Juulchin" (Tourist) Company and the 
American Compass Travel One. 
  The opening of the joint venture makes it possible to 
increase the amount of Mongolian tourists visiting the USA and 
is the first instance of capital investment made by a Mongolian 
organization in America. 
  At the opening ceremony there were taking part President of 
the "Juulchin" Company B. Delgersuren and the Ambassador of 
Mongolia to the USA L. Davaagiv. 

