<H3> <TI>   Prime Minister on Intention To Stabilize Economy </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW2302184594 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1648 GMT 23 Feb 
94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW2302184594 </F>
<F P=104>  Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, february23 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- The 
Prime Minister of Mongolia P. Jasray at the meeting with the 
representatives of Bayanhongor Aymag has announced about his 
intention to stabilize the country's economy on a sound ground. 
  As the prime minister noted, deficiency of goods is not felt 
in the country, despite high prices. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

