<H3> <TI>   MONTSAME Press Reviews Reported </TI></H3>
<H4>   Press Review for 23 Feb </H4>
<F P=102> OW2302184394 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1643 GMT 23 Feb 
94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW2302184394 </F>
<F P=104>  Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, February 23 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- Central 
Mongolian newspapers widely cover the official visit of the 
President of Mongolia P. Ochirbat to India. As the newspaper 
ARDIYN ERH informs, the President of India S. D. Sharma has 
accepted the invitation of the President P. Ochirbat to visit 
Mongolia. The newspaper particularly points out to the meeting 
of the President P. Ochirbat with the well-known Indian 
scientist-Mongolist K. Singh. As the newspaper informs, a group 
of experts of the Asian Development Bank has been to the country 
on a working visit. This bank grants a credit to Mongolia worth 
48.6 mln US dollars for development of telegraph communication. 
The newspaper notes that the credit is granted on the terms of 
development of competition in work of Mongolian communication 
organizations. 
  The newspaper publishes the answers of some members of the 
State Great Hural (SGH) the questions of the newspaper 
correspondent. They point out to the importance of propaganda of 
the new laws and provisions. 
  The newspaper publishes an article by lawyer S. Tsagaan 
about 
the constitutional court. The author stresses that foundation 
of the Constitutional Court is of great importance in activity 
of the state mechanism. 
  The government newspaper DZASGIYN GADZRYN MEUEE publishes an 
information about the meeting of the Prime Minister P. Jasray 
with the representatives of Bayanhongor Aymag. The newspaper 
notes that the prime minister has announced about his intention 
to stop economic deterioration and achieve stabilization of 
development of Mongolian economy. He noted that in the country 
deficiency of goods is not felt, despite high prices. 
  The newspaper publishes the government resolution about 
establishment of staffs and salaries of the state governing 
establishments, about measures on realization of the law on 
copyright. 

</TEXT>

